citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:45pm on 02 April
2025. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee by announcing their presence at the facility and via phone call. On
the phone call, the licensee confirmed no responsible adult was available. Failure to provide access to the facility,
animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in
enforcement action.
End Section

2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:45pm on 02 April 
2025. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee by announcing their presence at the facility and via phone call. On 
the phone call, the licensee confirmed no responsible adult was available. Failure to provide access to the facility, 
animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in 
enforcement action. 
 
 
End Section
